title: Domestic Producer Price Index (TURKSTAT - Turkish Statistical Institute)
text: ( Source : TURKSTAT - Turkish Statistical Institute ) Domestic producer price index increased by 1.53% Domestic producer price index (D-PPI) increased by 1.53% on monthly basis, increased by 7.81% on December of the previous year basis,
